msgctxt "sn12.13:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.13:0.2"
msgid "2. Āhāravagga "
msgstr "2. Fuel "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Samaṇabrāhmaṇasutta "
msgstr "13. Ascetics and Brahmins "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.15, sc1
msgctxt "sn12.13:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.13:1.2"
msgid "“Ye hi keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā jarāmaraṇaṃ nappajānanti, jarāmaraṇasamudayaṃ nappajānanti, jarāmaraṇanirodhaṃ nappajānanti, jarāmaraṇanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ nappajānanti; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are ascetics and brahmins who don’t understand old age and death, their origin, their cessation, and the practice that leads to their cessation. "

msgctxt "sn12.13:1.3"
msgid "jātiṃ … pe … "
msgstr "They don’t understand rebirth … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:1.4"
msgid "bhavaṃ … "
msgstr "continued existence … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:1.5"
msgid "upādānaṃ … "
msgstr "grasping … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:1.6"
msgid "taṇhaṃ … "
msgstr "craving … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:1.7"
msgid "vedanaṃ … "
msgstr "feeling … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:1.8"
msgid "phassaṃ … "
msgstr "contact … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:1.9"
msgid "saḷāyatanaṃ … "
msgstr "the six sense fields … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:1.10"
msgid "nāmarūpaṃ … "
msgstr "name and form … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:1.11"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ … "
msgstr "consciousness … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:1.12"
msgid "saṅkhāre nappajānanti, saṅkhārasamudayaṃ nappajānanti, saṅkhāranirodhaṃ nappajānanti, saṅkhāranirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ nappajānanti, "
msgstr "They don’t understand choices, their origin, their cessation, and the practice that leads to their cessation. "

#. VAR: brahmaññatthaṃ → brāhmaññatthaṃ (s1-3, km) | brahmaññathaṃ (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn12.13:1.13"
msgid "na me te, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samaṇesu vā samaṇasammatā brāhmaṇesu vā brāhmaṇasammatā; na ca pana te āyasmanto sāmaññatthaṃ vā brahmaññatthaṃ vā diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharanti. "
msgstr "I don’t regard them as true ascetics and brahmins. Those venerables don’t realize the goal of life as an ascetic or brahmin, and don’t live having realized it with their own insight. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn12.13:2.1"
msgid "Ye ca kho keci, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā jarāmaraṇaṃ pajānanti, jarāmaraṇasamudayaṃ pajānanti, jarāmaraṇanirodhaṃ pajānanti, jarāmaraṇanirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ pajānanti; "
msgstr "There are ascetics and brahmins who do understand old age and death, their origin, their cessation, and the practice that leads to their cessation. "

msgctxt "sn12.13:2.2"
msgid "jātiṃ … pe … "
msgstr "They understand rebirth … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:2.3"
msgid "bhavaṃ … "
msgstr "continued existence … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:2.4"
msgid "upādānaṃ … "
msgstr "grasping … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:2.5"
msgid "taṇhaṃ … "
msgstr "craving … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:2.6"
msgid "vedanaṃ … "
msgstr "feeling … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:2.7"
msgid "phassaṃ … "
msgstr "contact … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:2.8"
msgid "saḷāyatanaṃ … "
msgstr "the six sense fields … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:2.9"
msgid "nāmarūpaṃ … "
msgstr "name and form … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:2.10"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ … "
msgstr "consciousness … "

msgctxt "sn12.13:2.11"
msgid "saṅkhāre pajānanti, saṅkhārasamudayaṃ pajānanti, saṅkhāranirodhaṃ pajānanti, saṅkhāranirodhagāminiṃ paṭipadaṃ pajānanti, "
msgstr "They understand choices, their origin, their cessation, and the practice that leads to their cessation. "

msgctxt "sn12.13:2.12"
msgid "te kho me, bhikkhave, samaṇā vā brāhmaṇā vā samaṇesu ceva samaṇasammatā brāhmaṇesu ca brāhmaṇasammatā; te ca panāyasmanto sāmaññatthañca brahmaññatthañca diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharantī”ti. "
msgstr "I regard them as true ascetics and brahmins. Those venerables realize the goal of life as an ascetic or brahmin, and live having realized it with their own insight.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.13:2.13"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

